    "body": "It's not a bug in the compiler. On 0.8.x you just need to explicitly convert it to `uint32` first. See [How to convert bytes1 to int8 in Solidity?](https://ethereum.stackexchange.com/questions/111261/how-to-convert-bytes1-to-int8-in-solidity) for an explanation of a similar problem.",
